proDetail: 官方到货延迟，预计3月20日到货★付録　・３００キャラクターシール［特集］●大乱闘スマッシュブラザーズ　ＳＰＥＣＩＡＬ［企画］◆逆転裁判１２３　巧舟さん×岩元辰郎さん対談◆「ゼルダの伝説　コンサート２０１８」聴きどころ◆マッスルの闇鍋　リターンズ◆ＮＩＮＴＥＮＤＯ　６４がやってきた！　実物大図鑑◆キャラクターダービー　ＳＰＥＣＩＡＬ［新作ラインナップ］◆ヨッシークラフトワールド◆毛糸のカービィ　プラス◆スーパードラゴンボールヒーローズ　ワールドミッション…ほか雑誌: 100ページ出版社: 徳間書店言語: 日本語梱包サイズ: 26.1 x 21 x 0.6 cmNintendo DREAM2019年4月刊德间书店日文原版进口规格：平装100页，26.1 × 21 × 0.6 cm《Nintendo DREAM》（ニンテンドードリーム）是由日本德间书店发行的任天堂官方游戏杂志。该杂志在任天堂N64面世（1996年6月）时创刊，最初名为《The 64Dream》，后在2001年5月任天堂GameCube发售前更名，是一本关注任天堂各种主机以及诸多任天堂游戏的专门志。杂志除了介绍游戏相关攻略、活动、票选、行业发展等内容以外，还包括发行前独家预览以及开发者访谈等，并且每期附带一份游戏周边礼品，其中不限于海报、卡牌、CD、纪念册。

proDetail: Cook & Becker 出品* 2本游戏部族的主题配色笔记本；* 部族符号凹凸纹压印；* 约宽13cm×高21cm，PU精装，192页；* 内页印有16页《地平线：零之曙光》创作原稿；* 配有丝带书签与弹性封装绑带；* 附：Aoly官方原版艺术画一幅（30 x 22 cm）；* 附：定制铅笔两支、Aloy式回纹针一枚、笔夹一个、粉笔一支、地图一幅；* 精美外盒封装；* 限量1250套。These officia， limited-edition Horizon Zero Dawn notebooks have been made in conjunction with Guerrilla Game， the studio that created the PlayStation 4-exclusive video game Horizon Zero Dawn.Let yourself be creatively inspired with these notebooks based on the natural beauty of the world of Horizon Zero Daw， its inhabitant， and main character Aloy. These notebooks are perfect for both Horizon Zero Dawn fans and aficionados of notebook， and have been made with great care and attention. The notebooks have a considered and subtle design inspired by both the game and the artists behind it. Use them to let your own creativity flo， as well and record your thoughts. These notebooks make for an ideal gift for any Horizon Zero Dawn fan.Both notebooks feature hardcovers with rounded corner， while the paper inside is subtly lined. Several pages are printed with concept ar， sketches and textual observations exclusively produced by Guerrilla Games for these notebooks. The cover of the Limited Edition is made with uncoate， 85% recycled leather in the same natural color as the clothing of the Nora tribe featured in the game. A Banuk tribe sun symbol graces the front in a subtle blind emboss. The pen holder and the round closing elastic are produced in a color and material that hints at Aloy's bow and arrow. With the Limited Edition comes a pencil and paperclip of brushed aluminum in the shape of Aloy's Focus device.The special Collector's Edition consists of the Limited Edition noteboo， plus one extra hardcover notebook made with a dark brown 85% recycled leather. The spine is stitched with threads in the color of Aloy's outfi， and the front features the triangle symbol from Horizon Zero Dawn. This symbol forms the basis of the conography used in the world of Horizon. Its three sides stand for the three pillars of Horizon Zero Dawn: natur， machines and the tribe， with the marker in the middle representing Aloy as the game’s center point.A key piece of Horizon Zero Dawn concept artwork served as a guideline in the development of both notebook， and the Collector's Edition comes with a small Cook and Becker giclee print of this specific piece of ar， featuring Aloy. The Collector's Edition has the same accessories as the Limited Editio， but also includes a deep black graphite pencil and a separate pen clip with a leather strap and piece of blue chalk as a nod to the cave paintings in Horizon Zero Dawn. This blue color has also been carried through in some of the drawings on the inside of the notebooks.The Collector's Edition is presented in a handsome luxury box wherein the notebook， accessories and giclee print have been carefully placed.Details*  2 officially licensed notebooks*  13 W x 21 H cm | 5.1 x 8.3 inch*  Two hard cover notebooks with rounded corners*  Limited to ，250 copies*  Subtly line， pearl-colored 80 gsm paper*  192 pages*  A signature C&B design feature: a section of 16 pages of blank paper in the back for sketchingpurposes*  16 pages printed with original Horizon Zero Dawn concept art and sketches*  Both notebooks have an elastic closure with matching bookmarks*  Expandable inner pocket in the back*  Comes with an official giclee print of original concept art (size 30 x 22 cm)*  Wrapped in see-through paper and sealed with a sticker/label*  Packed in a luxury Collector's Box*  Accessories:	A custom pencil	A black graphite pencil	An aluminum paper clip in the form of Aloy's Focus device	A removable pen clip	A piece of triangle-shaped chalk	A printed world map

proDetail: Cook & Becker 出品* 含2本精装笔记本，深蓝+棕的杰洛特主题配色，白+棕的希里主题配色；* 符文凹凸纹压印；* 约宽13cm×高21cm，PU精装，192页；* 内页印有16页《巫师3：狂猎》创作原稿；* 配有丝带书签与弹性封装绑带；* 附：官方原版艺术画一幅（30 x 22 cm）；* 附：金属色铅笔一支、银色墨水笔一支、狼头金属徽章一枚；* 精美外盒封装；* 限量1250套。These officia， limited-edition Witcher notebooks are made in conjunction with CD Projekt RE， the developer of the acclaimed Witcher video game series.Step into the world of the Witcher with these notebooks based on the imager， storie， bestiary notes and the many spell and potion recipes Geralt finds during his adventures in The Witcher III: Wild Hunt. The notebook， with their design based on thevisual identity of the characters Geralt and Cir， are perfect for both fans of the Witcher and of beautifully designed notebooks. These notebooks are inspired by both the game and the artists that made the game. We invite you to use these notebooks to get creative yourself and note down your own thought， ideas and sketches! These notebooks make for an ideal gift for any fan of the Witcher game， or the novels that inspired them.Both notebooks feature hardcovers with rounded corner， with the paper inside subtly lined. Several pages contain concept art and sketches and textual observation， straight from the artists at CDPR. The visual inspiration for these notebooks comes from theiconic Witcher III key artwork 'Gerald and Ciri' – an image that also comprised part of Cook and Becker's The Witcher III fine art collection.The Limited Edition noteboo， with its deep-blue cover and brown spin， references Geralt's basic gear. For material we used bonded leather to provide a classical look. The symbols for Geralt’s five Signs used in The Witcher III: Wild Hunt have been blind embossed on the spine. Red is one of the Witcher's key brand colors and can be found in the closing elasti，the end papers and the reading ribbon of the Limited Edition.This notebook comes with three accessorie， amongst them a metal-colored pencil and a pen with silvercolored ink. These reference Geralt's two sword types: silver for monster， steel for men. One section in both notebooks has been made with black pape， a perfectsurface to run your silver pen over. A metal wolf’s head medallio， similar to that worn by Geral， completes this beautiful Witcher notebook.The special Collector's Edition consists of two notebooks: the Limited Edition notebook plus an extra notebook based on the character of Ciri. This notebook has been made with a white cotton fabric with subtle turquoise-colored details at the end papers and closing elasti， which makes it a perfect reference to Ciri's outfit. On the front we have reproduced one of the Witcher's rune patterns in a metallic foil. The spine is made with bonded leather blind embossed with both Geralt's and Ciri's sword sheath patterns.The artwork that visually inspired both notebooks is part of the Collector Edition in the form of a beautiful Cook and Becker giclee print.The Collector's Edition is presented in a handsome luxury box wherein the notebook， accessories and giclee print have been carefully placed.Details* 2 officially licensed notebooks* 13 W x 21 H cm | 5.1 x 8.3 inch* Two hard cover notebooks with rounded corners* Limited to ，250 copies* Subtly line， pearl colored 80 gsm paper* 192 pages* A signature C&B design feature: a section of 16 pages of blank paper in the back for sketchingpurposes* 16 pages printed with original concept art and sketches from The Witcher III: Wild Hunt* Both notebooks have an elastic closure with matching bookmarks* Expandable inner pocket in the back* Comes with an official giclee print of original concept art (size 30 x 22 cm)* Wrapped in see-through paper and sealed with a sticker/label* Packed in a luxury Collector's Box* Accessories:	A custom pencil	A pen with silver ink	A wolf’s head medallion

proDetail: 以制作高度像真珍藏人偶见称的知名珍藏人偶品牌Hot Toys 早前率先发布了首款PlayStation®4独占游戏《漫威蜘蛛侠》的蜘蛛侠1:6比例珍藏人偶，今天更抢先电玩游戏正式上架丶以Hot Toys自家创作的COSBABY设计，参照游戏中3款不同动态或装束的《漫威蜘蛛侠》蜘蛛侠打造成COSBABY (S) 迷你珍藏人偶，包括: 蜘蛛侠丶蜘蛛侠 (蹲伏版) 及蜘蛛侠 (庞克战衣版) ，让讨人喜欢的蜘蛛侠COSBABY再次施展飞檐走壁的蜘蛛异能，在现代丛林的纽约市中穿梭，打击恶势力维护市民安全！为配合蜘蛛侠角色在电影中各个飞檐走壁的高难度动作，因此特别为蜘蛛侠角色COSBABY装置磁铁，让粉丝们运用创意，可以将讨人喜欢的COSBABY融入日常生活当中，倍添趣味！3款《漫威蜘蛛侠》 蜘蛛侠COSBABY (S) 迷你珍藏人偶，高逾7.5cm 至16cm，每款蜘蛛侠COSBABY的幪头造型均选用弹性布料紧贴头形所缝制而成，并挂上浮夸的眼部表情，当中蜘蛛侠和蜘蛛侠 (蹲伏版) COSBABY是穿上红蓝双色的先进版战衣，胸口饰有标志性的白色蜘蛛图案，分别摆出经典发射蜘蛛丝手势和蹲伏姿态，不论细节与卖相都十分讨好；而蜘蛛侠 (庞克战衣版) COSBABY则以富有街头摇滚风格造型示人，头上添有仿金属锅钉细节，蜘蛛侠战衣上穿上牛仔背心与红色波鞋，背上一支饰有蜘蛛网纹的红色结他，左手握住蜘蛛丝模拟飞荡姿态，造型型格独特，摇滚味十足！名称：《漫威蜘蛛侠》蜘蛛侠(庞克战衣版) COSBABY迷你珍藏人偶尺寸：高约16cm可动关节：bobblehead (摇头) 元素特点：COSBABY珍藏人偶将各式各样帅气英挺的电影角色化身为可爱的Q版人物，继续以可爱的baby form形态及bobblehead (摇头) 元素呈现，俘虏所有超级英雄粉丝。*详细以官方到货实物为准

proDetail: ソルジャー76、出動する。世界的大ヒットを記録したアクションシューティングゲーム『オーバーウォッチ』からのねんどろいど第9弾は、「ソルジャー76」です！フル可動仕様のソルジャー76は、マスクも取り外せるので、滅多に見ることのできない素顔を楽しむことができます。彼の大きな特徴の一つである、背中にプリントされた「76」の文字もしっかりペイントしています。各スキルを再現する豊富なパーツは、デフォルメしながらも可能な限り作中の造形、塗装を施しています。ヘリックスロケットは専用支柱で自由に設置可能。バイオテックフィールドも付属するので、他のねんどろいどと組み合わせ、体力を回復している状況を再現できます。アルティメットスキルのタクティカルバイザーはクリアパーツで造形されており、マスク部分を専用のパーツに付け替える仕様になっています。また、ゴルフクラブも付属するので、チャーミングなヴィクトリーポーズも楽しめます。続々と登場するオーバーウォッチシリーズのねんどろいどで、さまざまな組み合わせをお楽しみ下さい！士兵：76，出击。创下了全球销量纪录的动作射击游戏『守望先锋』的粘土人第9弹「士兵：76」登场！采用超可动式样的士兵：76，可将面具取下，得以看到平时难得一见的本来面貌。作为他的一大特征，其背后的「76」两个编号也进行了清晰的印制。丰富的配件可以再现各种技能，尽可能地在Q版化之后还原游戏中的造型以及涂装。螺旋飞弹可以利用专用支柱自由设置位置。生物力场配件也附带在內，与同系列的其他粘土人组合在一起，可以再现与队友一同恢复体力的场景。终极技能战术目镜采用透明素材打造，可用专用配件来替换面具部分。另外还附带高尔夫球棒，迷人的胜利姿势值得期待。请和陆续登场的其他守望先锋角色粘土人组合在一起一起玩耍吧！手办材质：ABS&PVC制 涂装完成品尺寸比例：非标准比例·附带专用底座·全高：约100mm原型制作：トイテックD.T.C制作协力：Nendoron实物与照片可能稍有不同
